%%R
# Normalization
set.seed(55063)
clusters <- quickCluster(germcells)
germcells <- computeSumFactors(germcells, cluster = clusters)
germcells <- logNormCounts(germcells)

set.seed(55063)
mod_mf <- modelGeneVar(germcells)
hvgs_mf <- getTopHVGs(mod_mf, var.threshold = 0)
length(hvgs_mf)

# Dimensionality reduction
set.seed(55063)
germcells <- runPCA(germcells, subset_row = hvgs_mf)

# Identify HVGs based on sample
set.seed(55063)
mod_mf_batch <- modelGeneVar(germcells, block = colData(germcells)$Sample)
hvgs_mf_batch_all <- getTopHVGs(mod_mf_batch, var.threshold=0)
hvgs_mf_batch_5percent <- getTopHVGs(mod_mf_batch, prop = 0.05)
print(length(hvgs_mf_batch_all))
print(length(hvgs_mf_batch_5percent))

germcells_corrected <- fastMNN(germcells, subset.row = hvgs_mf_batch_5percent, batch=germcells$Sample, BPPARAM = MulticoreParam(workers = 12))#

germcells_corrected <- runTSNE(germcells_corrected, dimred = "corrected", perplexity=300, num_threads = 24, verbose = F)

reducedDim(germcells, "mnnTSNE") <- reducedDim(germcells_corrected, "TSNE")
